  ('social-worker-moex-02901', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-102-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '相較於商品品質，對於社會服務品質的特性之敘述，下列何者是正確的？', '["品質可事先預測並獲得保證", "涉入的利害關係人及其動機較為單純", "品質創造滿足和需求後可能造成資源排擠", "主要以一般社會大眾為對象"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f9469744500c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07df2aebbe74", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "111", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02902', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-102-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列對於各種決策模式的相關敘述，何者是正確的？', '["垃圾桶決策模式（garbage can model）視決策為一種理性且結構化的過程", "滿意模式（satisficing model）是一種高度理性的決策模式", "漸進模式（incrementalist model）被視為是一種理性的決策模式", "非理性決策模式（non-rational decision making model）即是針對複雜的、不確定性情況所發展出來的決 策模式"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f9469744500c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07df2aebbe74", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "111", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02903', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-102-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '有系統地蒐集、分析與工作相關的資訊，並就「工作內容」、「工作脈絡」、「工作條件」予以清楚描述 的途徑和過程，稱之為「工作分析」（job analysis）。請問下列何者不適合運用在工作分析之方法上？', '["觀察法（observation method）", "技術會議法（technical conference method）", "日誌法（diary method）", "問卷法（questionnaire method）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f9469744500c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07df2aebbe74", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "111", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02904', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-102-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '由於「人」是組織最重要的資產，因此社會福利組織如何透過人才培訓，找到對的人，做對的事，成為 組織重要的競爭優勢。根據英國人事與發展學會（Institute of Personnel and Development, IPD）調查顯示： 具有競爭力的人力資源必須具備那四項特性，才能因應外在環境的變化及競爭？', '["有價值、普遍性、容易模仿、能夠凸顯", "有價值、稀少性、不易模仿、能夠整合", "有價值、稀少性、容易模仿、能夠凸顯", "有價值、普遍性、不易模仿、能夠整合"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f9469744500c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07df2aebbe74", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "111", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02905', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-102-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '主管在對員工進行評估時，會以員工的某項特性（例如人際關係）來推論其工作表現與績效，此種情況 稱為：', '["暈輪效應（halo effect）", "偏見（leniency or strictness）", "偏誤（bias）", "刻板印象（stereotyping）"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f9469744500c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07df2aebbe74", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "111", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02906', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-102-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '每一個機構針對某項職務大多有該項職務的工作執掌說明書。請問工作職掌說明書是經過下列那項工作 之後得來的？', '["設定個人績效考核標準", "工作規範分析", "工作分析", "分析工作條件"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f9469744500c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07df2aebbe74", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "111", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 20, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02907', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-102-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '為了改善現職社會工作員的工作表現，因而設計一些能提升社會工作技能的學習活動，這種人力資源管 理的活動稱為：', '["訓練", "發展", "教育", "績效考核"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f9469744500c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07df2aebbe74", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "111", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 21, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02908', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-102-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作員有倦怠感已成為普遍現象。管理者為了避免工作越來越專門化和例行化，將許多小型任務合 併成較大型的工作，如此可讓工作範圍更大並更具多樣化，因而可減少對工作的厭倦感。這樣的做法稱 為：', '["工作輪調", "工作豐富化（job enrichment）", "工作擴大化（job enlargement）", "工作再適應"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f9469744500c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07df2aebbe74", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "111", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02909', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-102-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '隨著夫妻雙薪家庭的增加，員工對於彈性工作制度的需求也增加。由於社會工作實務中，社工員需要與 案主直接面對面接觸，若管理者考慮給予社會工作員彈性工作安排，較佳的方式是採用：', '["電傳工作", "彈性工時", "按件計酬", "帶薪休假"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f9469744500c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07df2aebbe74", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "111", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02910', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-102-f2e04173', 'sub-social-worker-05', NULL, 'single_choice', '目前社會福利機構越來越重視績效導向與預算導向，造成社會工作督導的功能偏向那一項功能？', '["教育性功能", "行政性功能", "支持性功能", "轉換性功能"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:14+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "f9469744500c", "answer_pdf_sha1": "07df2aebbe74", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "102030", "c": "111", "s": "0703", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作管理", "year": "102", "exam_name": "102年第一次專技醫師中醫師分試中醫師營養師心理師醫事檢驗師護理師社會工作師、特考聽力牙體語言治療師考試", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL)
